          "Trust/Society/Club: registered trust deed/bye-laws, registration certificate, resolution of trustees/managing committee. Funds can only be used for stated objects",
          "Power of Attorney (POA): account holder authorises another person to operate — bank verifies POA document carefully, registers it",
